The former Acting Chairman APC Caretaker Extraordinary Convention Planning Committee and Niger state Governor, His Excellency, Mohammed Sani Bello, today led other members of the committee to welcome His Excellency Governor Mai Mala, who returned from a medical trip in the United Arab Emirates. Governor Bello said the committee was at the Yobe state Governorâ€™s Lodge to welcome Gov. Buni and to brief him on the affairs of the party while he was away. He said based on the transmission of power to him by Gov. Buni, the committee commenced the process of the convention slated for 26th March 2022. Responding, Governor Buni commended Members of the Caretaker Committee for the support and cooperation extended to the Acting Chairman while he was away. He assured that the March 26th Convention dateline remains sacrosanct and solicited for support for a successful convention. Governor Buni also described members of the committee as very committed to the ideals of the party and a spirit of teamwork for the success of the party.